1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,980
[Episode 55]

2
00:00:07,910 --> 00:00:08,790
Lagi lihat apa?

3
00:00:13,470 --> 00:00:14,350
Maaf.

4
00:00:18,630 --> 00:00:20,630
Maaf, aku sudah
salah paham padamu.

5
00:00:21,750 --> 00:00:22,630
Maaf

6
00:00:23,670 --> 00:00:25,070
aku nggak memercayaimu.

7
00:00:27,230 --> 00:00:28,310
Dan juga, maaf,

8
00:00:29,550 --> 00:00:31,410
hari itu aku memakimu
gitu dengan

9
00:00:32,549 --> 00:00:34,210
kata-kata
yang sangat kasar.

10
00:00:35,070 --> 00:00:37,070
Sean sudah kasih tahu
aku semuanya.

11
00:00:43,830 --> 00:00:44,150
Hm,

12
00:00:44,150 --> 00:00:46,010
pagi ini kau
pasti kehujanan, ya?

13
00:00:47,030 --> 00:00:47,630
Lalu,

14
00:00:47,630 --> 00:00:48,960
apa guru belum kembali?

15
00:00:51,390 --> 00:00:52,920
Mungkin pergi
makan siang.

16
00:00:53,590 --> 00:00:55,190
Aku keluar carikan
guru buatmu dulu,

17
00:00:55,190 --> 00:00:57,120
lalu sekalian
belikanmu makanan.

18
00:00:57,910 --> 00:00:58,790
Terima kasih.

19
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:12,870
Ada apa
dengan bocah itu?

20
00:01:19,430 --> 00:01:20,430
Sudah kembali?

21
00:01:23,470 --> 00:01:24,350
Dingin.

22
00:01:24,950 --> 00:01:25,830
Dingin sekali.

23
00:01:36,630 --> 00:01:37,630
Terima kasih, ya.

24
00:01:38,430 --> 00:01:39,870
Gimana? Sudah baikan?

25
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:41,970
Kalau gitu,

26
00:01:41,990 --> 00:01:43,390
kau sudah selesai makan?

27
00:01:44,390 --> 00:01:44,950
Ya.

28
00:01:49,990 --> 00:01:50,350
Nih.

29
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:51,880
Untukmu.

30
00:01:58,990 --> 00:01:59,720
Lapar nggak?

31
00:02:00,350 --> 00:02:01,410
Mau makan cokelat?

32
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:28,900
[Bersambung]

